data.description: Exquisite 3BR/2.5BA residence in the prestigious Eagle Landing. Crafted in 2022, this contemporary masterpiece defines luxury living. Revel in the opulence of granite kitchen countertops, a stainless double oven, and an expansive pantry for culinary connoisseurs. The master suite is a haven with 'his & hers' closets, dual sinks, a sumptuous soaking tub, and a separate shower. Two bonus rooms offer versatile spaces for home offices or hobbies. Experience the perfect blend of modern design and community amenities of Eagle Landing, including a pool, golf, gym, and more. Conveniently located minutes away from upscale shopping, fine dining, and top-tier schools. This is not just a home; it's a modern sanctuary in a prime Florida locale—your dream home awaits.
